No. 09-8958. Stephen Crump, Petitioner v. Superior Court of California, Alameda County. 559 U.S. 1058, 130 S. Ct. 2348, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 2995.

176 L. Ed. 2d 577,

April 5, 2010.

Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Justice Breyer took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
